---

#### 🧩 Использование

 \`\`\`html
 <ss-lib-icon
    [icon]="IconType.Search"
    [height]="'32'"
    [width]="'32'"
    [color]="Colors.IconSecondary"
 ></ss-lib-icon>
  \`\`\`
